Doc Spatz,<br>
     It was Dr. Hang S. Ngor.  Two youths from an Asian gang were arrested.  The motive appeared to be robbery.  They knew nothing of his past, his role in the movie, his own fight for freedom.  It's a dirty rotten shame.                                                                          I don't believe we have said it all either.  There is so much there for many of us, that it takes a while for it all to come out, providing we're prepared to articulate what's inside.  Every so often, through these past months, something buried in some nook or cranny of my soul or spirit gets unearthed, and the words come tumbling out for better or worse. 
